Install this packages on Debian:

    $ sudo apt-get install python-sphinx texlive-xetex texlive-latex-recommended texlive-latex-extra lmodern ttf-wqy-microhei

To generate HTML:

    $ make html

To generate PDF:

    $ make latexpdf

To use livereload(https://github.com/mockko/livereload), install `python-pip`, and run:

    $ pip install livereload
    $ make livehtml

To generate CHM, install `fp-utils`, and run:

    $ make chm

Tested with `python-sphinx 1.1.3` and `texlive 2012.20120611` on Debian unstable.

To use other CJK fonts, modify `latex_elements` option in source/conf.py. For more info, read http://mirrors.ctan.org/macros/xetex/latex/xecjk/xeCJK.pdf
